oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Man adding crappie to string in Cherokee Lake, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of unidentified man that is adding one more crappie to the string that already has four fish on it in Cherokee Lake. Man is in fishing boat wearing cap and jumpsuit. There are reeds next to the boat and the shoreline with trees on the ridge in the background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
